c 'hmbqkKgfp'
store(zemedeKeysKaIbExtended) 'ሙቡቁኩኹጉፉፑ'
store(zemedeGeez)  'ᎀᎄቈኰዀጐᎈᎌ'
store(zemedeKaIb)  'ᎃᎇቍኵዅጕᎉᎍ'
