c ---------------------End Labiovelars----------------------------------------------------------

c ---------------------Maps for Numbers---------------------------------------------------------
store(ArabOnes)    '23456789'
store(ones)        '፪፫፬፭፮፯፰፱'
store(tens)        '፳፴፵፶፷፸፹፺'
